name: May Him rest His holy eyes
description: Started from a photo of the full moon out of the small portion of sky I can see from my bedridden spot; shining Dark Light over my alter and opened urn. A lot of people didn't appreciate how beautiful something like that was, and even scorned me for daring share such a beautiful moment with them. How do you like His holy gaze staring into your Souls now? You fucks. He thirsts for a blood price to be paid in tithes for your sins, and it's not coming from those who helped set Him to rest.
